---
title: Jalapeño Popper Beef Burgers with Sweet Potato Rounds
description: This classic appetizer just got upgraded to the burger section of the menu! Cream cheese, cheddar cheese and jalapeños, juicy beef burgers and sweet potato rounds create this lip-smacking explosion of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF210301_R20_W16_CA_RP153157-1_KB_Main_low-15619caa.jpg
